headline.print_headline: Federal Judge Strikes Down Alaska Gay Marriage Ban
headline.main: Federal Judge Strikes Down Alaska Gay Marriage Ban

lead_paragraph: A federal judge on Sunday struck down Alaska's first-in-the-nation ban on gay marriages, the latest court decision in a busy week for the issue.
